dct_title_s: The "lower road to Princeton" : a map showing the main country roads of to-day, and by a dotted line the route taken by General Washington and his army on the night of January 2, 1777
dct_description_sm: C.S. Sincerbeaux, Princeton Class of 1902. Historic Maps copy has ms. annotations.
